Rulings.Base:
1. You cannot activate this card during the Damage Step.
2. This card does not target.
3. Removing the monsters from play starts a Chain.
4. You activate the effect to remove the monsters during the Damage Step at the same time Flip Effects are activated and resolved.
5. This effect won't apply to any Psychic-Type monster that is not face-up on your side of the field when this card resolves.
6. If a Psychic-Type monster you controlled when this card resolved is flipped face-down and then attacked, the effect to remove the monsters from play won't activate.
